---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.jsx';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Our Story | YourHQ"
  description="Founder-led. Built in Whangārei. We help Kiwi business owners own their digital space — without the homework."
>
  <Navbar client:load />

  <main class="bg-paper min-h-screen">

    <!-- HEADER -->
    <section class="pt-32 pb-20 border-b border-carbon bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center">

            <!-- Header Text -->
            <div class="lg:col-span-7">
                <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter leading-[0.9] mb-8">
                    Founder-led. <br/>
                    <span class="text-signal">Built in Whangārei.</span>
                </h1>
                <div class="max-w-xl border-l-4 border-carbon pl-8 py-2">
                    <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium leading-relaxed text-carbon">
                        We help Kiwi business owners own their digital space — without the homework.
                    </h2>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Header Image -->
            <div class="lg:col-span-5">
                <div class="aspect-[4/3] bg-gray-100 border-2 border-carbon shadow-hard transform rotate-2 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-500 overflow-hidden rounded-sm">
                    <img
                        src="/nic-lian-laugh.webp"
                        alt="Nic and Lian laughing together"
                        class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-500"
                    />
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 1: WHY YOURHQ EXISTS -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-paper border-b border-carbon">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 leading-relaxed text-lg text-carbon/90 space-y-8">

            <div class="mb-12">
                <span class="text-sm font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-signal mb-2 block">The Problem</span>
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-carbon">Why YourHQ Exists</h2>
            </div>

            <p>
                YourHQ exists because too many brilliant small business owners are doing everything right… except the online part.
            </p>
            <p>
                Not because they don't care — because they're busy.
            </p>
            <p>
                And the options out there are rough:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                <li>DIY tools that turn into a months-long after-hours project</li>
                <li>Agencies that cost a fortune, take forever, and often disappear after launch</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                So I built a system that makes this feel like relief:
            </p>

            <div class="border-l-4 border-signal pl-6 py-2">
                <p class="font-bold text-xl text-carbon mb-2">Websites built fast. Kept sorted. Looked after long-term.</p>
                <p>Built in 5 days. No homework. No tech jargon.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 2: THE GOOGLE TEST -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-white border-b border-carbon">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 leading-relaxed text-lg text-carbon/90 space-y-8">

            <div class="mb-12">
                <span class="text-sm font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-signal mb-2 block">The Truth</span>
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-carbon">The Google Test Is Real.</h2>
            </div>

            <p>
                When someone's choosing between two businesses, they Google both names.
            </p>
            <p>
                One looks established. One looks risky.
            </p>
            <p>
                It's not fair — but it's real.
            </p>

            <div class="bg-paper p-8 border border-carbon shadow-sm">
                <p class="font-medium text-lg">
                    YourHQ exists to make sure your online presence matches the quality of your work — so you don't lose jobs to businesses that simply look bigger online.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 3: HOW IT STARTED -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-paper border-b border-carbon">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 leading-relaxed text-lg text-carbon/90 space-y-8">

            <div class="mb-12">
                <span class="text-sm font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-signal mb-2 block">Origin</span>
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-carbon">How It Started</h2>
            </div>

            <p>
                I started learning to code while doing my Master's and kept coming back to one question:
            </p>
            <p class="font-bold text-xl text-carbon">
                How do we get busy, capable business owners online — properly — without adding more work to their plate?
            </p>
            <p>
                Most people don't need "a website project." They need the website problem gone.
            </p>
            <p>
                So I productised the process:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                <li>One short phone chat</li>
                <li>We pull what we need from your existing footprint</li>
                <li>We build it in 5 days</li>
                <li>Then we stay on as caretakers so it doesn't rot</li>
            </ul>

            <div class="border-l-4 border-carbon pl-6 py-2">
                <p class="font-bold text-xl text-carbon">That's the whole model.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 4: THE VALUES -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-white border-b border-carbon">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 leading-relaxed text-lg text-carbon/90 space-y-8">

            <div class="mb-12">
                <span class="text-sm font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-signal mb-2 block">Values</span>
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-carbon">What We Care About</h2>
            </div>

            <p>
                We're not here to impress other designers. We're here to help you win.
            </p>
            <p>
                That means:
            </p>

            <div class="space-y-4">
                <div class="bg-paper p-6 border border-carbon">
                    <p><strong>No homework</strong> — you're not writing website copy at midnight</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-paper p-6 border border-carbon">
                    <p><strong>No ghosting</strong> — we stay on after launch</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-paper p-6 border border-carbon">
                    <p><strong>Ownership</strong> — you own your domain, content, and design from day one</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-paper p-6 border border-carbon">
                    <p><strong>Care</strong> — your site stays fast, current, and looked after</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 5: MEET THE TEAM -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-paper border-b border-carbon">
        <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-16 text-center">Meet The Team</h2>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-start">

                <!-- LIAN -->
                <div class="space-y-6">
                    <div class="aspect-[4/5] bg-gray-100 border border-carbon shadow-hard relative overflow-hidden mb-6 group">
                         <img
                            src="/lian-headshot.webp"
                            alt="Lian Passmore"
                            class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
                        />
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-carbon">Lian</h3>
                        <span class="text-signal font-bold tracking-wide uppercase text-sm">Founder & Lead Developer</span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="text-lg text-carbon/90 space-y-4 leading-relaxed">
                        <p>
                            I own YourHQ and lead the builds — strategy, copy, design, infrastructure, performance.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            If it's on your site, I'm accountable for it.
                        </p>
                        <div class="bg-white p-4 border-l-2 border-carbon">
                            <span class="font-bold block mb-1">What I bring:</span>
                            A calm, capable process that turns your story into a website that feels like you — and works while you sleep.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- NIC -->
                <div class="space-y-6">
                    <div class="aspect-[4/5] bg-gray-100 border border-carbon shadow-hard relative overflow-hidden mb-6 group">
                        <img
                            src="/nic-headshot.webp"
                            alt="Nic"
                            class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
                        />
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-carbon">Nic</h3>
                        <span class="text-signal font-bold tracking-wide uppercase text-sm">Client Partnerships & First Contact</span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="text-lg text-carbon/90 space-y-4 leading-relaxed">
                        <p>
                            Nic is your first point of contact — questions, pricing, bookings, and making sure the process feels simple from day one.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            She'll help you figure out which package fits, and she'll keep you out of the weeds.
                        </p>
                        <div class="bg-white p-4 border-l-2 border-carbon">
                            <span class="font-bold block mb-1">What she brings:</span>
                            Clarity, warmth, and straight answers — without the jargon.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 6: WHY WHANGAREI -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-carbon text-paper border-b border-carbon">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center space-y-8">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white">Based in Whangārei. Built for NZ-wide.</h2>

            <div class="text-lg text-gray-300 space-y-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                <p>
                    We're based in Whangārei, and we work with businesses all over New Zealand.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Because the process doesn't require meetings or travel — just a phone call and a few texts.
                </p>
                <p class="font-bold text-white text-xl">
                    Same speed. Same care. Same outcome.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 7: CTA -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-8 text-carbon">Ready to Meet Us?</h2>

            <div class="space-y-4 mb-12 text-lg text-carbon/80">
                <p>Questions? Chat with Nic. Ready to build? <strong>Let's get you sorted.</strong></p>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-6 mb-8">
                <div class="inline-block p-1 border-2 border-dashed border-gray-400 rounded-full">
                    <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-signal hover:bg-red-600 text-white font-bold py-4 px-12 rounded-full transition-all transform hover:scale-105 shadow-hard">
                        Let's Chat
                    </a>
                </div>
                <a href="/pricing" class="text-lg font-bold text-carbon hover:text-signal transition-colors duration-300">
                    View Pricing &rarr;
                </a>
            </div>

            <p class="text-sm text-carbon/50">Founder-led, supported by real humans — and built to last.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>